{"type": "article", "id": 29187, "title": "看图：这里是过去24小时内发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。PS：我们认为这个世界的重要性不应该有绝对的等级，重点是看得更多，探索更多。", "date": "2016-07-06T02:33:17Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 5, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160706102617oHEce04fSPlKkUdp.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><h3>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h3><p class=\"\"><b>1、南方多地洪涝灾害</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706092115lvfCtWPaTjygusr7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">长江日报 贾代腾飞/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">武汉，连日暴雨使张沉堤进洪口闸出现洪水漫堤，消泗乡 14 个村的村民连夜紧急乘坐巴士转移。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706092213IEPlaesOZCF69xyd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666276\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">陈力/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">安徽省舒城县，人们将生猪从猪舍中牵出赶上检疫车。此前，这六千多头生猪由于环保和防疫等限制而无法转移。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>2、美国民众在国会山静坐要求枪支管控</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706091254kugQCOzeMdtyB5cW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Mark Wilson/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">美国华盛顿，枪击案受害者家属在国会山圆形大厅静坐示威，要求枪支管控。<b><br></b></p><p class=\"\"><b>3、2016 美国总统大选</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706093030bVrMI6RQoGkwWLFe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634273\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Brian Snyder/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">美国北卡罗来纳州夏洛特（Charlotte），美国总统奥巴马首次助阵民主党总统候选人希拉里的竞选集会。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>4、西班牙动物权益者“浴血”示威</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070609161457HGfWIaFgxPLZOJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748792\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Eloy Alonso/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">西班牙潘普洛纳（Pamplona），奔牛节前一天，动物权益者在身上涂抹红色颜料示威，要求废止斗牛活动。<b><br></b></p><p class=\"\"><b>5、委内瑞拉举行阅兵庆祝独立日</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607060937153eac7iZEROmzhpDL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Carlos Jasso/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">委内瑞拉加拉加斯，当地举行大阅兵，庆祝委内瑞拉独立 205 周年。<br></p><h3>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h3><p><b>1、2016 秋冬巴黎高定时装周</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706095208UqMxf0dI9AaDEk4z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">FRANCOIS GUILLOT/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">Chanel 品牌秀场。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706095412A4BrjmGkIUNyLe8C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665584\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">BERTRAND GUAY/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">Giorgio Armani Prive 品牌秀场。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070609580347Wfu8y6xCzHLjPO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Timur Emek/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706095845dpUsXCJDqO5hjaNi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Timur Emek/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706100118bUHJKmoFLCGuVX4E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Timur Emek/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">街头潮人云集。</p><p><b>2、雨过天晴后的晚霞</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706101624EGUwJkZcq9dLtzlo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">张锁庆/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">处在黄梅季尾声的上海迎来今夏首个高温天。傍晚时分，市区雨过天晴，绚丽的晚霞和华灯初上的街道交相辉映。<br></p><p><b>3、以色列空降兵参加跳伞训练</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706102317LCiRSF5J9NPt08lK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Amir Cohen/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">以色列特拉维夫，以色列空降兵在特拉维夫市附近帕勒马希姆空军基地（Palmachim）参加跳伞训练。<br></p><p><b>4、土耳其穆斯林民众祷告迎接开斋节</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706093946bA70jXonEIilrCL1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651694\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Murat Kula/Anadolu Agency/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">土耳其安卡拉，穆斯林民众祷告庆祝开斋节到来。<b><br></b></p><p><b>5、熔岩与星空</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706094609VQgN4WqhXZf1Psxt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665414\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Sutanta Aditya/Barcroft Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">印度尼西亚卡罗，星空下的印尼锡纳朋火山。5 月 22 日，锡纳朋火山爆发，至少造成 7 人死亡，2 人受伤。<br></p>"}